---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection';
import Reviews from '../../components/Reviews';
import ServiceForm from '../../components/ServiceForm';
import LicenseBadges from '../../components/LicenseBadges.astro';
import BrandsSection from '../../components/BrandsSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Air Conditioning Repair Los Angeles | HiLo Heating and Air" description="Expert AC repair, AC installation, and heating repair in Los Angeles. Fast, reliable HVAC service from licensed technicians at HiLo Heating and Air.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Air Conditioning Repair Los Angeles</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">LA's weather is its own kind of strange — bone-dry heat in one neighborhood, ocean fog rolling into another the same afternoon. Whatever your system's dealing with, HiLo Heating and Air covers it.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-10 pb-4 sm:py-16 sm:pb-6 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <LicenseBadges />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-10 items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Schedule Service</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Get a Free Estimate</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Fill out the form and our team will get back to you within 15 minutes. Same-day service available.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Same-Day Service Available</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Free Diagnostics with Repair</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Upfront Pricing, No Hidden Fees</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ServiceForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">HVAC Services in Los Angeles</h2>

        <p>LA's weather is its own kind of strange — bone-dry heat in one neighborhood, ocean fog rolling into another the same afternoon. Whatever your system's dealing with, HiLo Heating and Air covers it: <strong>air conditioning repair Los Angeles</strong> homeowners need in July, <strong>furnace repair Los Angeles</strong> residents call for in January, and everything connected to keeping a system running well in between.</p>

        <h2>One Call Covers the Whole System</h2>
        <p>A lot of companies pick a lane — cooling specialists who shrug at furnaces, or heating guys who barely touch AC units. We don't work that way. The same techs handling <strong>air conditioning repair Los Angeles</strong> calls all summer are the ones doing <strong>heating repair Los Angeles</strong> households need once it cools off. One number, year-round, instead of juggling two different companies depending on the season.</p>

        <h2>When Repair Stops Making Sense</h2>
        <p>Sometimes a unit's just done. If your AC's pushing fifteen years and needs a repair every other summer, replacement usually saves more money long-term than another patch job. That's where <strong>AC installation Los Angeles</strong> comes in — not as an upsell, but as the honest recommendation when repair costs start rivaling a new system. We'll always tell you straight which way it leans before pushing anything.</p>

        <h2>What Actually Breaks Most Often</h2>
        <p>On the cooling side: dead capacitors, dirty coils, refrigerant leaks, compressors that have simply worn out. That covers most <strong>air conditioning repair Los Angeles</strong> visits — weak airflow, short cycling, bills that creep up with no clear cause.</p>
        <p>Furnaces fail differently. A pilot light that won't hold, a blower motor grinding louder than it should, an ignitor that's quit, or — less common but more serious — a cracked heat exchanger. A good share of <strong>furnace repair Los Angeles</strong> calls start with someone noticing an odd smell when the system kicks on, which is always worth checking right away.</p>
        <p>When it's not a full breakdown but the heat's just inconsistent room to room, that's usually <strong>heating repair Los Angeles</strong> territory — ductwork, a miscommunicating thermostat, sometimes just an aging system losing efficiency.</p>

        <h2>Fast Turnaround, No Runaround</h2>
        <p>Nobody wants to wait a week with no AC or no heat. Most repair and <strong>AC installation Los Angeles</strong> appointments get scheduled same-day or next-day, and trucks carry the parts that get used most, so jobs typically wrap in one visit.</p>

        <h2>Local Crews Who Know the City</h2>
        <p>LA's a sprawling place — older homes in some neighborhoods, newer construction in others, each with different ductwork quirks and permitting requirements. Being local means we've already seen most of it. Every job, whether it's repair or full <strong>AC installation Los Angeles</strong> projects, gets done to code and backed by a guarantee.</p>
        <p>If your system's struggling — cooling, heating, or somewhere in between — call HiLo Heating and Air. We'd rather get it right the first time.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <Reviews client:visible />
    <BrandsSection />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you handle both AC and furnace work, or just one?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Both — same technicians do cooling and heating, so it's one company year-round.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How fast can someone come out for AC repair?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually same-day, sometimes next-day during busy stretches.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">My AC's old and keeps breaking. Repair again or replace?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Depends on age and repair history — we'll give an honest read before recommending installation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Will I get a price before any work starts?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, always upfront, no surprises on the invoice.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Is a permit needed for new AC installation?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually, yes — we handle that process as part of the job.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">My furnace smells off when it starts. Serious?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Worth checking right away — could be dust, could be something more serious like a heat exchanger issue.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How often should systems get inspected?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Once a year each, ideally before the relevant season hits.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are technicians licensed and insured?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Every one of them, fully licensed and insured.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">HiLo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
